      "topConceptOf": "https://schema.stage.datacite.org/linked-data/vocab/resourceTypeGeneral",
      "scopeNote": "Artifacts, specimens, material samples, and features-of-interest of any size. Digital representations of physical objects should use one of the other resourceTypeGeneral values.",
